{"tid":1200360,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"應急藥物清單","createTime":"2019-06-10T17:33:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T08:48:41.000Z","uid":258348,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"9f4fb75f45864fad4aadc04d9e963d33e6bc4a56","tid":1200360,"uid":258348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T17:33:43.000Z","msg":"提供物質嘅巴絲可以諗諗買啲基本藥物<br />\n利申 澳洲註冊藥劑師<br />\n注意事項：<br />\n買嘅時候可以問有無平啲嘅牌子！功效一樣，淨係牌子/製造商唔同<br />\n以下全部藥物都可以係藥房買到（萬寧屈臣氏可能要問藥劑師）<br />\n1. 必利痛 Panadol - Paracetamol 500mg 止痛藥<br />\n- 每次 500mg-1000mg<br />\n- 每4-6小時一次 <br />\n- 每24小時最多4g<br />\n2. Ibuprofen 200-400mg 消炎藥<br />\n- 每次 200-800mg<br />\n- 每8小時一次<br />\n- 每24小時最多3200mg<br />\n- 最好食啲野，會削胃<br />\n- 受傷後2天內可以食減少紅腫，但係之後就唔建議，會減慢康復速度<br />\n- 缺水時不建議服用（如腹瀉）<br />\n3. Fexofenadine 180mg 或者 Loratadine 10mg 抗敏感藥<br />\n- 理論上一日一次，但係可以隔12小時一次<br />\n- 敏感例如皮膚過敏、鼻敏感等等都可以用<br />\n- 對比下呢兩隻係極少機率眼訓<br />\n4. Emla / Xylocaine Gel 麻醉藥膏<br />\n- 少量就有效，可以用作止痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 約30分鐘後有效，之後可以以清水沖走多餘藥膏<br />\n- 價錢可能比較昂貴<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n集思廣益，有其他意見或者問題可以下面問"},{"pid":"df283b15f10191f56821389da8d6e7e1d5b92317","tid":1200360,"uid":258348,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T17:43:11.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d16af49a5e27b51032f5f4cedb08bdf160913b4","tid":1200360,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df283b15f10191f56821389da8d6e7e1d5b92317","tid":1200360,"uid":258348,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T17:43:11.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T17:44:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.g